{"tid":1945794,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"消息指食肆明日傍晚起限食客人數 多種娛樂場所要關閉","createTime":"2020-03-27T09:33:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-27T09:50:33.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1fddc4a2c6b294e56ab3419739992da1c71bd2f3","tid":1945794,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T09:33:58.000Z","msg":"消息指食肆明日傍晚起限食客人數 多種娛樂場所要關閉<br />\n<br />\n行政會議下午舉行特別會議，消息指，多項措施會在明天下午六時實施，食肆人客數目限於座位半數或以下，枱與枱之間要保持1.5米距離，每張枱限坐四人，客人進入食店時必須帶口罩，食店要為客人量體溫、預備搓手液。措施維持14日，政府會為食肆提供補償。<br />\n<br />\n消息指，政府亦會規定明天傍晚六時起，關閉遊戲機中心、浴室、健身中心、兒童遊樂場、戲院等公共娛樂場所，另外Party Room等出租娛樂場所亦要關閉，為期14天，政府亦會提供補償。政府亦正研究，禁止四人以上的群眾聚集，預計短期內推出措施，但公共交通將獲豁免，「紅白二事」等亦會有較寬鬆安排。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1276840&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1276840%26csid%3D261_341&d=UCgs38VSsqZrRa6JqpzgNmaNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=d95f799c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1276840&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"1317fdc6b6c00a17c0d90412cd9cf56e628ed5ec","tid":1945794,"uid":24036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T09:36:59.000Z","msg":"紅事算9數 改期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n白事就無得好講姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a86bedc6a21119cfec7c9f8eed1b3985449a533","tid":1945794,"uid":14494,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T09:39:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">公共交通將獲豁免</span><br />\n好彩仲有得番工<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c870fac716e796fcd614ebf0906e0b9732ad5f73","tid":1945794,"uid":8572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1317fdc6b6c00a17c0d90412cd9cf56e628ed5ec","tid":1945794,"uid":24036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T09:36